WE HAVE A LOT OF FOOTAGE GOING ALL THE WAY BACK TO '96.

472
00:29:08,470 --> 00:29:10,580
THIS IS HIS FIRST PRESS CONFERENCE

473
00:29:10,590 --> 00:29:12,110
RIGHT AFTER THE PLANE CRASH.

474
00:29:12,130 --> 00:29:13,890
