477
00:29:17,920 --> 00:29:19,420
HE SHOULD BE OUT OF SURGERY BY THEN.

478
00:29:19,450 --> 00:29:22,130
YOU'RE VERY CLOSE TO TOM,AREN'T YOU?

479
00:29:22,260 --> 00:29:24,560
HE'S HELPED ME TREMENDOUSLY.

480
00:29:25,290 --> 00:29:26,650
SINCE THE HURRICANE?

481
00:29:27,690 --> 00:29:30,360
I CAN PUT SOMEONE ELSE ON THIS

482
00:29:30,400 --> 00:29:32,220
IF YOU DON'T THINK YOU CAN BE OBJECTIVE.

483
00:29:32,740 --> 00:29:34,150
NO. I CAN BE OBJECTIVE.

484
00:29:35,520 --> 00:29:37,370
I'LL WANT TO SEE IT BEFORE IT RUNS

485
00:30:25,890 --> 00:30:27,440
THANK YOU FOR BRINGING ME HERE.

486
00:30:39,600 --> 00:30:41,400
-I HAVE TO GO.
-I KNOW.

487
00:30:44,470 --> 00:30:46,200
I WANT YOU TO REMEMBER THIS.

488
00:30:47,230 --> 00:30:50,120
NO MATTER WHAT HAPPENS IN THE FUTURE,REMEMBER THIS.

489
00:30:50,680 --> 00:30:53,960
REMEMBER HOW IT WAS WHEN WE FIRST MET.

490
00:30:57,340 --> 00:30:57,810
TOM...

491
00:30:57,830 --> 00:30:59,140
THERE'S GONNA BE A LOT OF ROUGH DAYS AHEAD,

492
00:30:59,170 --> 00:31:00,190
A LOT OF CHANGES.

493
00:31:00,580 --> 00:31:02,790
THE ONLY WAY THAT WE'LL GET THROUGH IT...

494
00:31:05,110 --> 00:31:07,130
IS IF WE REMEMBER.

495
00:32:33,570 --> 00:32:34,580
HI.

496
00:32:38,680 --> 00:32:39,780
YOU'RE HERE?

497
00:32:41,190 --> 00:32:42,240
SO ARE YOU.

498
00:32:45,290 --> 00:32:48,190
YOU SAVED ME...AGAIN.

499
00:32:50,460 --> 00:32:51,710
YOU SAVED YOU.

500
00:32:52,400 --> 00:32:54,270
THE DOCTORS SAY THEY'VE NEVER SEEN A BODY

501
00:32:54,330 --> 00:32:55,510
FIGHT SO HARD TO LIVE.

502
00:32:56,070 --> 00:32:57,450
YOU'RE ALREADY HEALING,TOM.

503
00:32:57,830 --> 00:32:59,560
YOU GAVE ME YOUR BLOOD?

504
00:33:03,510 --> 00:33:05,570
HOW DID YOU KNOW THAT'S WHAT I NEEDED?

505
00:33:06,840 --> 00:33:08,130
I DIDN'T.

506
00:33:12,740 --> 00:33:14,380
WHERE'S MY CLOTHES?

507
00:33:16,250 --> 00:33:17,330
THEY'RE IN MY OFFICE.

508
00:33:17,420 --> 00:33:20,540
MY KEYS... SHOULD BE WITH THEM.

509
00:33:20,810 --> 00:33:24,660
GET MY KEYS... AND GO HOME.

510
00:33:26,080 --> 00:33:27,020
WHY?

511
00:33:27,060 --> 00:33:29,050
'CAUSE I WANT YOU TO GET ME SOMETHING...

512
00:33:29,910 --> 00:33:31,460
FROM THE CLOSET.

513
00:33:32,560 --> 00:33:33,740
WHAT'S IN IT?

514
00:33:35,550 --> 00:33:36,960
EVERYTHING.

515
00:33:50,120 --> 00:33:52,650
THEIR REPORT IS TWO MINUTES,AND THEN WE GO LIVE!

516
00:33:52,760 --> 00:33:56,620
ALL RIGHT! HEY,HE MADE IT,YOU KNOW? UNDERLAY.

517
00:33:56,700 --> 00:33:58,830
JUST CAME OVER THE WIRE,HE MADE IT THROUGH SURGERY.

518
00:33:58,890 --> 00:34:00,200
I THINK YOU MIGHT WANT TO LEAD WITH THAT...

519
00:34:00,250 --> 00:34:02,640
UNLESS YOU GOT SUSPECTS YOU WANT TO TALK ABOUT.

520
00:34:02,670 --> 00:34:03,110
DO THE POLICE EVEN HAVE ANY SUSPECTS?

521
00:34:03,110 --> 00:34:04,180
LARKIN!

522
00:34:04,860 --> 00:34:06,580
GO SET UP,I'LL CATCH UP TO YOU.

523
00:34:06,600 --> 00:34:07,650
LOOK,YOU CAN'T DO THIS.

524
00:34:08,480 --> 00:34:10,620
-I HAVE TO.
-NO,I JUST GOT BACK FROM HEALY'S.

525
00:34:10,880 --> 00:34:12,500
RUSSELL,I DON'T EVEN KNOW WHO THIS HEALY PERSON IS.

526
00:34:12,600 --> 00:34:13,840
OKAY,IT DOESN'T MATTER,ALL RIGHT?

527
00:34:13,910 --> 00:34:15,280
THE BOTTOM LINE IS IF YOU GO PUBLIC WITH THIS,

528
00:34:15,300 --> 00:34:16,100
NO ONE'S GONNA BELIEVE YOU

529
00:34:16,150 --> 00:34:17,710
BECAUSE NO ONE'S GONNA BACK THE STORY.

530
00:34:17,960 --> 00:34:20,290
YOU WERE RIGHT ALL ALONG. THE MILITARY IS INVOLVED.

531
00:34:20,400 --> 00:34:21,860
SO YOU'RE NOT GONNA BE SAVING ANY LIVES

532
00:34:21,890 --> 00:34:24,510
BY TALKING NOW,LARKIN,BUT YOU MIT BE KILLING US.

533
00:34:24,540 --> 00:34:26,460
THERS A GUY OUT HERE THAT DOESN'T WANT THIS STORY TOLD.

534
00:34:26,480 --> 00:34:29,940
I UNDERSTAND HOW IMPORTANT IT IS TO YOU TO PROTECT MARIEL,I DO.

535
00:34:29,960 --> 00:34:31,340
NO,IT'S NOT ABOUT MARIEL ANYMORE.

536
00:34:31,390 --> 00:34:32,930
BUT I CAN'T WORRY ABOUT HER ANYMORE.

537
00:34:33,020 --> 00:34:37,150
I HAVE TO WORRY ABOUT US AND OUR BABY.

538
00:34:37,700 --> 00:34:39,960
AND I'M SORRY IF THIS MEANS

539
00:34:39,990 --> 00:34:41,350
THAT THE KIDS ARE GOING TO GET HURT.

540
00:34:41,380 --> 00:34:44,350
IT'S GONNA HURT ALL OF US,NOT JUST THE KIDS,LARKIN.

541
00:34:47,920 --> 00:34:49,310
I HAVE TO DO THIS.

542
00:35:09,580 --> 00:35:10,770
I'LL BE RIGHT OUTSIDE.

543
00:35:11,240 --> 00:35:12,130
THANK YOU.

544
00:36:30,340 --> 00:36:33,890
-I WAS SO SCARED,DADDY.
-I KNOW. I'M SORRY...

545
00:36:34,990 --> 00:36:36,180
FOR EVERYTHING.

546
00:36:36,270 --> 00:36:39,320
YOU LOOK AMAZING,TOM. I CAN'T BELIEVE YOU WERE SHOT.

547
00:36:39,470 --> 00:36:41,030
I APPRECIATE YOU GUYS HANGIN' AROUND,

548
00:36:41,070 --> 00:36:42,800
BUT IT'S GETTIN' KINDA LATE,YOU KNOW?

549
00:36:43,400 --> 00:36:45,220
MAYBE YOU OUGHTA BE GETTIN' HOME.

550
00:36:45,710 --> 00:36:48,520
SHERIFF,MR. VARON WOULD LIKE TO SEE YOU.

551
00:36:48,930 --> 00:36:50,090
SEND HIM IN.

552
00:36:53,230 --> 00:36:56,060
HEY. WE TRIED TO FIND YOU.

553
00:36:58,210 --> 00:37:00,070
CAN YOU GUYS GIVE US A MINUTE?

554
00:37:00,270 --> 00:37:01,960
EVERYBODY WAS JUST TAKING OFF.

555
00:37:02,070 --> 00:37:04,510
ALL RIGHT,GOOD NIGHT. I'LL SEE YOU ALL SOON.

556
00:37:05,010 --> 00:37:07,880
GOOD NIGHT,BABE. GOOD-BYE,JESS.

557
00:37:07,910 --> 00:37:09,030
GOOD NIGHT,TOM.

558
00:37:18,500 --> 00:37:20,320
TOM,I NEED YOU TO DO SOMETHING FOR ME.

559
00:37:21,430 --> 00:37:23,070
MY WIFE'S ABOUT TO GO LIVE WITH A STORY

560
00:37:23,130 --> 00:37:24,620
I DON'T THINK YOU WANT TOLD,

561
00:37:25,420 --> 00:37:27,010
A STORY BIGGER THAN YOUR SHOOTING.

562
00:37:28,160 --> 00:37:30,060
AND FOR NOW,IT'S A STORY I'M WILLING TO KEEP TO MYSELF,

563
00:37:30,150 --> 00:37:31,600
BUT I'M GONNA NEED YOUR HELP.

564
00:37:40,900 --> 00:37:42,010
IS THAT THE BACKGROUND YOU WANT?

565
00:37:42,100 --> 00:37:43,310
-YEAH,THIS LOOKS GREAT.
-ALL RIGHT.

566
00:37:43,450 --> 00:37:45,850
AND SO WE'RE GOOD,TWO MINUTES OR SO.

567
00:37:45,960 --> 00:37:49,070
LARKIN.DID YOU HEAR TOM'S GONNA BE ALL RIGHT?

568
00:37:49,110 --> 00:37:51,140
YEAH,IT'S GREAT NEWS.

569
00:37:57,610 --> 00:38:01,470
LARKIN,LOOK... HE'S A GOOD MAN.

570
00:38:02,450 --> 00:38:04,280
I KNOW YOU'VE PROBABLY HEARD A LOT OF STRANGE THINGS

571
00:38:04,300 --> 00:38:05,960
ABOUT BOTH OF US LATELY,

572
00:38:07,100 --> 00:38:08,450
BUT HE'S A GOOD MAN.

573
00:38:10,120 --> 00:38:11,420
90 SECONDS.

574
00:38:12,330 --> 00:38:13,030
YEAH.

575
