576
00:38:15,420 --> 00:38:18,290
-UH,HE'S INSIDE.
-MARIEL?

577
00:38:19,140 --> 00:38:22,510
I WAS GOING THROUGH SOME VIDEO FOOTAGE TONIGHT,

578
00:38:22,550 --> 00:38:23,560
AND I...

579
