AND I SAW YOU...

580
00:38:26,970 --> 00:38:29,380
HERE,ABOUT NINE YEARS AGO...

581
00:38:30,740 --> 00:38:31,970
WITH TOM.

582
00:38:33,320 --> 00:38:36,910
I DIDN'T REALIZE YOU TWO WENT SO FAR BACK.

583
00:38:39,490 --> 00:38:44,250
YOU WERE STILL MARRIED TO RUSSELL THEN,WEREN'T YOU?

584
00:38:48,770 --> 00:38:50,390
I WAS.

585
00:38:51,910 --> 00:38:53,470
HE'S A GOOD MAN,TOO.

586
00:38:55,680 --> 00:38:56,670
YEAH.

587
00:38:58,150 --> 00:39:01,330
YOU KNOW I HAD A SECRET ABOUT WHO I AM,

588
00:39:01,420 --> 00:39:03,260
I BEGGED HIM TO KEEP FOR ME...

589
00:39:04,990 --> 00:39:06,380
BUT HE WOULDN'T DO IT.

590
00:39:07,800 --> 00:39:10,060
HE TOLD YOU BECAUSE YOU WERE MORE IMPORTANT.

591
00:39:17,510 --> 00:39:18,430
HEY,LARKIN.

592
00:39:19,390 --> 00:39:22,010
WE'RE GONNA GO LIVE IN ABOUT TEN SECONDS. I'M SORRY.

593
00:39:25,870 --> 00:39:27,920
IN EIGHT,SEVEN,

594
00:39:28,870 --> 00:39:30,400
SIX... YEAH.

595
00:39:30,610 --> 00:39:32,040
FIVE...

596
00:39:32,570 --> 00:39:38,490
FOUR,THREE,TWO,ONE.

597
00:39:48,790 --> 00:39:50,160
<i>WHEN YOU THINK OF ALL THIS MAN HAS BEEN THROUGH,</i>

